message:
Implement screen shaking on the map screen

I also renamed SetDisplay{X,Y} to SetPosition{X,Y} because otherwise

    SetDisplayX(x);
    if (x != GetDisplayX()) {
        This would be possible
    }

Actually, those two functions are only used by Game_Player::Center
which could logically be moved to Game_Map anyway.

Follow instruction to build and launch the project

The instructions :

Warning:Native C/C++ source code is found, but it seems that NDK option
is not configured.  Note that if you have an Android.mk, it is not used
for compilation.  The recommended workaround is to remove the default
jni source code directory by adding:
 android {
    sourceSets {
        main {
            jni.srcDirs = []
        }
    }
}
to build.gradle, manually compile the code with ndk-build, and then
place the resulting shared object in src/main/jniLibs.
